id: pmc-nh7q
title: Prepend mode duplicates Keep a Changelog bracketed release sections
description: "GitHub issue unbraind/pm-changelog#9: pm-changelog --mode prepend must replace existing Keep a Changelog bracketed release headings such as ## [2026.5.24] - 2026-05-24 when generated headings use ## 2026.5.24 - 2026-05-24, preserving older release history for consumers like pm-cli."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[3]: changelog,keep-a-changelog,release
created_at: "2026-05-24T14:16:18.072Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-24T14:18:13.681Z"
author: codex-changelog-verify
resolution: fixed
expected_result: pm-changelog --mode prepend replaces equivalent Keep a Changelog bracketed release headings and preserves older release sections.
actual_result: Regression test passes; release scripts/workflow now use prepend mode; local check/test/audit/pack gates passed.
comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-24T14:17:51.637Z",codex-changelog-verify,"Evidence: fixed mergeChangelog/--mode prepend to normalize generated and Keep a Changelog bracketed release headings; updated upstream release workflow/scripts to prepend; npm run check, npm test, npm audit --omit=dev, and npm pack --dry-run all passed locally."
